thread.title: Jonathan Minor

author: Jonathan Minor
title: Jonathan Minor
text: Great quality prints at an exceptional price. I have ordered more prints on canvas because of my positive experience. My order was processed immediately, and was shipped out the door on the next business day. I was very impressed with the speed of service and quality printing. The prints were well wrapped and protected... even my family (parents and grandparents) commented on how well the canvases were wrapped. I will continue to order these kinds of pictures from canvasdiscount.
